            <title>[LU-13555] Do not treat repo ml kernels as &apos;special&apos; just map them to RHEL</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13555</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Do not treat repo ml kernels as &apos;special&apos; just map them to RHEL&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Currently the lustre-build-linux.m4 check for ELRepo mainline kernel build check maps to MAINLINE_KERNEL but it is cleaner to simply map them to RHEL_KERNEL and discard the special redundant test.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
